        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Promoting Opportunities in Skilled Trades Act or the POST Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows recipients of existing federal career and technical education funds to use those funds to raise awareness for skilled trade programs and other programs that prepare students for in-demand occupations.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
